                     <interp inst="t18290115-203-person1640" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I took the prisoner in charge with the property; I searched him, but found nothing on him.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>The prisoner pleaded poverty.</p>
